RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER.EVENT_SEQ_NO = LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT.EVENT_SEQ_NO AND OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER.VERSION_NO = LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT.VERSION_NO

LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTBS_PARTICIPANT_RATIO.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT.EVENT_SEQ_NO = LBTBS_PARTICIPANT_RATIO.EVENT_SEQ_NO AND LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT.CONTRACT_TYPE = LBTBS_PARTICIPANT_RATIO.CONTRACT_TYPE AND LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT.DRAWDOWN_NO = LBTBS_PARTICIPANT_RATIO.DRAWDOWN_NO AND LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT.PARTICIPANT = LBTBS_PARTICIPANT_RATIO.CUSTOMER_NO

LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTBS_PART_SETTLE_CURR_DET.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT.PARTICIPANT = LBTBS_PART_SETTLE_CURR_DET.PARTICIPANT AND LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT.CONTRACT_TYPE = LBTBS_PART_SETTLE_CURR_DET.CONTRACT_TYPE

LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT.CONTRACT_REF_NO = OLTBS_CONTRACT_ENTITY.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT.CONTRACT_TYPE = OLTBS_CONTRACT_ENTITY.CONTRACT_TYPE AND LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT.DRAWDOWN_NO = OLTBS_CONTRACT_ENTITY.DRAWDOWN_NO AND LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT.PARTICIPANT = OLTBS_CONTRACT_ENTITY.CUSTOMER_NO

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT SSI_MNEMONIC, SETTLEMENT_SEQ_NO SEQ_NO, BRANCH, PAY_ACCOUNT, RECV_ACCOUNT, COUNTERPARTY AGENT, CURRENCY FROM OLTMS_INSTR WHERE COUNTERPARTY IN (?, 'ALL') and branch in (GLOBAL.current_branch, 'ALL') and module in (?, 'AL') and product_code in (?, 'ALL') AND currency in (?, '*.*') AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM olvws_PROD_ACNT_Access X WHERE (PAY_ACCOUNT = X.AC_GL_NO or RECV_ACCOUNT = X.AC_GL_NO) AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ?)
SELECT distinct c.ccy_code, c.ccy_name FROM cytms_ccy_defn c

select a.entity_id, b.entity_name, b.entity_type, b.PHONE_NO, b.FAX_NO, b.EMAIL from oltbs_contract_entity a, oltms_customer_entity_details b where contract_ref_no = decode(?, 'TR', ?, 'DR', ?, ?) and event_seq_no = (select max(event_seq_no) from oltbs_contract_entity where contract_ref_no = decode(?, 'TR', ?, 'DR', ?, ?) and contract_type = decode(?, 'TR', 'FC', 'DS', 'TR', 'DR', 'TR') and drawdown_no = 0) and contract_type = decode(?, 'TR', 'FC', 'DS', 'TR', 'DR', 'TR') and drawdown_no = 0 and a.customer_no = ? and b.customer_no = a.customer_no and b.entity = a.entity_id and not exists (select 1 from oltbs_contract_entity c where c.contract_ref_no = ? and c.event_seq_no = ? and c.contract_type = ? and c.drawdown_no = ? and c.customer_no = ? and c.entity_id = a.entity_id) UNION select b.entity, b.entity_name, b.entity_type, b.PHONE_NO, b.FAX_NO, b.EMAIL from oltms_customer_entity a, oltms_customer_entity_details b where a.customer_no = ? and a.record_stat = 'O' and a.auth_stat = 'A' and b.customer_no = a.customer_no and not exists (select 1 from oltbs_contract_entity c where contract_ref_no = ? and event_seq_no = ? and contract_type = ? and drawdown_no = ? and customer_no = ? and c.entity_id = b.entity)
select customer_no, customer_name1 from oltms_customer where once_auth='Y' and record_stat='O' and auth_stat='A'
SELECT FIELD_NAME, FIELD_DESC FROM OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS WHERE FIELD_TYPE = 'BA' and field_name ='BAPRODUCT' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O'AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'

SELECT SSI_MNEMONIC, SETTLEMENT_SEQ_NO SEQ_NO, BRANCH, PAY_ACCOUNT, RECV_ACCOUNT, COUNTERPARTY AGENT, CURRENCY FROM OLTMS_INSTR WHERE COUNTERPARTY IN (? , 'ALL') and branch in (GLOBAL.current_branch, 'ALL') and module in (?, 'AL') and product_code in (?, 'ALL') AND currency in (?, '*.*') AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM olvws_PROD_ACNT_Access X WHERE (PAY_ACCOUNT = X.AC_GL_NO or RECV_ACCOUNT = X.AC_GL_NO) AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ?)
